        <p class="default">
            <span class="default">Janet: Does moon have an effect on our health in any other way?</span></p>
        <p class="default">
            <span class="default"><i>Dai </i>: No, not that we know of.</span></p>
        <p class="default">
            <span class="smltxt2">The <i>dais</i> spoke for 10 minutes about the moon&#8217;s effect
                on the conception of the boy child. Janet tried to steer the conversation away from
