        <p class="default">
            <span class="default">Janet: Do <i>bhoot-pret </i>(spirits) enter the body through the
                skin like they say the Mata pox or measles comes through the skin?</span></p>
        <p class="default">
            <span class="default">Harbans Kaur: No, spirits do not effect through the skin but we
